{"tid":2220854,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人父母一藍一黃","createTime":"2020-09-28T03:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T02:21:04.000Z","uid":31521,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c036c573d99985c9f21ca35c2496a7980d0357f7","tid":2220854,"uid":31521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:20:31.000Z","msg":"我就係 父母都係藍領<br />\n老豆日日講大陸對香港幾好 帶幾多錢落嚟<br />\n成日屌示威搞到公司冇生意 返工俾人阻 幾多人失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後懶中立話政府係做錯 但我哋都只可以做順民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老母初期都話自己係中立 但都有望住電視屌狗<br />\n721之後直情話自己係黃 繼續屌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日同老豆嘈大陸有幾賤幾虛偽<br />\n又覺得俾大陸狗恰到上心口 後生仔爭取民主反抗好合理<br />\n仲要日日放工就上YouTube睇燒生 吳明德呢類kol<br />\n好多時我老豆唔夠佢講 望住佢黑晒面真係好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566aa09f0a80c17c852aef0b83eea5245bd88ab6","tid":2220854,"uid":320041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"兩個都黃<br />\n<br />\n老母每日聽黃kol 5-6個鐘<br />\n搞到冇時間理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630d2e83e2ef3074fc3b6e578df133eebd554f52","tid":2220854,"uid":31521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"566aa09f0a80c17c852aef0b83eea5245bd88ab6","tid":2220854,"uid":320041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"兩個都黃<br />\n<br />\n老母每日聽黃kol 5-6個鐘<br />\n搞到冇時間理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:26:18.000Z","msg":"巴打就好，全家同聲同氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54910fa39bfda702ebc2d48ca72dd61f580cb5a","tid":2220854,"uid":71596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:57:20.000Z","msg":"老母是本身是港豬<br />\n而家雖然都是 但會屌大陸同黑警 <br />\n老母是深藍 <br />\n但我是家中唯一獨子 所